verbose_text: Data show that GSPE prevents the changes of histopathology and biomarkers in heart, kidney, and liver tissues of the mice exposed to TiO 2 nanoparticles (NPs); grape seed procyanidin extract prevents the majority of tissue and molecular damage resulting from NP treatment.
